{"tid":1674780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"水門海南雞&清玉 周邊商鋪","createTime":"2019-10-25T11:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T17:15:07.000Z","uid":220008,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"003f8ecb08b9d63508b609e89573d981ec98456d","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"首先<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人既行動力真係好強</span></span><br />\n作為住元朗既香港人 岩岩就已經去左懲罰佢地<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔算真係好多人排 目測30人左右 <br />\n本身又新街果個位好闊<br />\n但係中間開撚左檔賣電話卡既阻撚左半條街<br />\n變相手足排隊就逼哂係條5米闊既鋪口位<br />\n人多好自然就會企左係隔離鋪出面<br />\n咁清玉隔離果間海味舖就叫人唔好企係佢鋪口<br />\n（唔算冇禮貌）<br />\n重點黎啦：<br />\n人地兩間鋪帶旺左你個場 你仲叫人唔好阻9住你鋪口  <br />\n個陣又唔係有人睇緊你間鋪d貨 果個位又咁窄 <br />\n唔明點解唔可以比人企過少少 又唔係企滿你鋪口 係香港人就唔該唔好咁少氣啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要妒忌別人比你有勇氣！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSnNOQy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSnNOQy.png&h=9585f823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身都係2 3個人企左係左邊（點阻左佢？）<br />\n佢D貨咁又算唔算阻街？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ovNJ6DB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FovNJ6DB.png&h=88e56421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個位排檔 係黑社會比佢排定係佢係黑社會？ <br />\n<br />\n利申本人試過問電話卡價 條廢老串77 又話唔比影相（睇樣可能都有份721）<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"6b29d1d42eea4ef4ad4a003647e24365de3e25be","tid":1674780,"uid":219216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"由佢講 睇下生意邊個好"},{"pid":"d8eba09db287418c3c4f9f5cb442b701b4b43761","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"有冇人知個電話卡廢老有冇份721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee45b9cc13c428a1c952d6c3ad8b410351b6a124","tid":1674780,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:59:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"646f8930e9439fe43b5ebd4b9f13dafb97bfbb68","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:01:11.000Z","msg":"我等清玉杯野飲 等左20分鐘左右 佢就叫人唔好企係鋪出面5 6次 佢間鋪烏蠅都冇隻 唔係咁都阻到你做生意啊？？？"},{"pid":"20ca832e41da483cd61145db7d5f71ee443ceb71","tid":1674780,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />海味鋪唔恨得咁多 佢又唔係熟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce10a69f11e1cb8ffb1a4a9f892f76a4ba748563","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"你唔撚係要人排出馬路啊？？"},{"pid":"45d540ed442caba61fce3d7ebae91e0fc6993f1d","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"如果呢條電話卡佬係有份721 搵人幫佢執靚個檔口 唔好咁撚兜繆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f61d8121876510b90695e097e5f50f8010823399","tid":1674780,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbfba9e230010510c30ca52ab9c4df1b674b6d6","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"有冇手足幫手起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67e1dbedb