b71100f61dc4","tid":1674780,"uid":57287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"752e8314c6b81c63364c521b35850a632481b0bf","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:03:42.000Z","msg":"元朗人唔好幫呢條廢老買電話卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:39:40.000Z","msg":"買過一次 都唔撚係做生意既<br />\n十問九唔應又冇禮貌 啲卡又貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:43:28.000Z","msg":"諗住影下佢張死人報價牌 DKLM佢話唔影得 你咁撚驚比人格價 你就咪撚寫出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85035122df7bf148e85ade3908803ca5dfa11ee","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721唔見人<br />\n831打死人<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"fa52f21c6c40b411f27e67a931af215758c5182c","tid":1674780,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"003f8ecb08b9d63508b609e89573d981ec98456d","tid":1674780,"uid":220008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:54:47.000Z","msg":"首先<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人既行動力真係好強</span></span><br />\n作為住元朗既香港人 岩岩就已經去左懲罰佢地<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔算真係好多人排 目測30人左右 <br />\n本身又新街果個位好闊<br />\n但係中間開撚左檔賣電話卡既阻撚左半條街<br />\n變相手足排隊就逼哂係條5米闊既鋪口位<br />\n人多好自然就會企左係隔離鋪出面<br />\n咁清玉隔離果間海味舖就叫人唔好企係佢鋪口<br />\n（唔算冇禮貌）<br />\n重點黎啦：<br />\n人地兩間鋪帶旺左你個場 你仲叫人唔好阻9住你鋪口  <br />\n個陣又唔係有人睇緊你間鋪d貨 果個位又咁窄 <br />\n唔明點解唔可以比人企過少少 又唔係企滿你鋪口 係香港人就唔該唔好咁少氣啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要妒忌別人比你有勇氣！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZSnNOQy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZSnNOQy.png&h=9585f823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身都係2 3個人企左係左邊（點阻左佢？）<br />\n佢D貨咁又算唔算阻街？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ovNJ6DB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2